<figureCitation id="13032A5A361CFFA265D9FC8BD2459598" box="[1239,1307,871,896]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="14.[151,250,1055,1077]" captionTargetBox="[286,1302,197,1033]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[280,1310,193,1038]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 8. Historical and new records of Arichlidon watsonae n. sp., Bhawania cf. goodei, Chrysopetalum elegantoides, C. maculata and C. occidentale in the Tropical Eastern Pacific. Empty symbols indicate previous records." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2609684/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
